snippet.title: Aircar Update Cinematic Trailer
snippet.description:
Aircar is a simple immersive flying experience built for VR.

Aircar is turning two in August and is getting an update. This update adds vertical takeoff and landing, landing pads, graphical improvements and bug fixes. Aircar is available for free on Steam VR and the Oculus store. 

*This cinematic trailer contains high quality post process effects like motion blur and lens flares that are not present in the actual game. It was rendered in real time using the actual game environment in the Unreal Engine.
